tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE community_consultations (
  consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  theme VARCHAR(255),
  feedback TEXT,
  participant_name VARCHAR(100),
  participant_contact VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE community_consultations (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  topic TEXT,
  organizer TEXT,
  location TEXT,
  start_date TIMESTAMP,
  end_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  consultation_id INT,
  participant_name TEXT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  submitted_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ethical_concerns (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  concern TEXT,
  description TEXT,
  consultation_id INT,
  resolved BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE community_consultations (
  consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  consultation_topic VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  consultation_date DATE,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  organizer_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  participant_email VARCHAR(255),
  consultation_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (consultation_id) REFERENCES community_consultations(consultation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_id INT,
  concern_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES participants(participant_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (concern_id) REFERENCES ethical_concerns(concern_id)
);
